Manage Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) and Identity and Access Management (IAM) roles.

Usage:
  confluent iam rbac role [command]

Available Commands:
  describe    Describe the resources and operations allowed for a role.
  list        List the available RBAC roles.

Global Flags:
  -h, --help            Show help for this command.
      --unsafe-trace    Equivalent to -vvvv, but also log HTTP requests and responses which may contain plaintext secrets.
  -v, --verbose count   Increase verbosity (-v for warn, -vv for info, -vvv for debug, -vvvv for trace).

Use "confluent iam rbac role [command] --help" for more information about a command.
